This chart supports Ingress resources. If an Ingress controller, such as [nginx-ingress](https://hub.kubeapps.com/charts/stable/nginx-ingress) or [traefik](https://hub.kubeapps.com/charts/stable/traefik), is installed in the cluster, that Ingress controller can be used to serve your MinIO(R) server.

To enable Ingress integration, set the *ingress.enabled* parameter to *true*, and *disableWebUI* to *false*.
